apple or google login in financial sector
2022-06-03 03:21:54
"Simple question I have that I can't seem to find the answer to. Why don't we see financial services companies use Apple ID or Google ID for login methods? I've looked at Amex, BofA, Chase, Ally, Axos, and others, and none of them seem to give you the option to signup or signin with either Apple ID or Google ID. Is there some regulation around this that prevents that sector from using this?"
"['The concern isn’t just the authentication part of it, but also the information they’d get access to. (Read some of the fine print)']"
